Text: Uhm, I haven't yet listened to the entire album yet. However from what I have heard, while the quality is good, track number 3, paranoia, is not complete. It's like 2 minutes, when the song should be 3:37. It cuts off. Could you please re-upload? Or maybe it's a problem on my end (which i doubt)? Or at the very least upload just that song individually so I can add it into the album. It's bothering me having an incomplete song.
